~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : promote                                   ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : promote <username>

   This promotes a user to the next level up. You can only promote a 
   user of a lower level than yourself up to your own level.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : demote, pop
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

